name: Y0u 4r3 D4t4
description: We live in a modern age, where privacy, one of the most important civil liberties we have, is seriously threatened. For the powerful, we are more data in a table than people on our feet. This piece is a mirror to see ourselves through their eyes. With our faces showing the same code that builds the running application, the code exposes itself for the ones who look in the mirror. @RodrigoFavarete
